1. Backend receives POST request with data:
- auth_token (must belong to an admin)
- name (string)
- city (string)
2. Verify that the auth_token belongs to an admin.
3. Check if a team with the exact same name and city already exists in the `teams` table to prevent duplicates.
4. Insert a new record into the `teams` table:
- set `name`
- set `city`
5. Return ok.
